{"tid":1811124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德信中學男教師以「曱甴」形容示威者　校董會勒令停職 14 日兼扣薪","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T12:52:39.000Z","uid":226984,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eebd89c81568f663697621926d1e0dcad4abc32b","tid":1811124,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山德信中學一名男教師，上個月被指以粗口訓斥學生，言談間又以「曱甴」形容示威者，校方當時表示會就事件作出紀律研訊。校長羅春平今日發表聲明，指法團校董會議勒令該老師由 1 月 3 日起停職 14 天，停職期間須扣薪，以作警誡。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，法團校董會認為該老師不應在任何情況下使用粗言穢語，「利用社會事件比喻學生學習亦極不恰當」。校董會並且裁定該老師「違反本校職員行為守則」，已發出書面警告，並且「嚴重訓示」他不要再犯，「如有再犯，該老師會被立即解僱」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，該名老師同意校方給予校董會的事件報告內容，並且「樂意接受懲處，深表悔意」，承諾日後不會再違反職員行為守則。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，身為教育工作者，「每一位老師必須保持良好的個人品德，並遵從嚴格的教育操守」。對於社會上政治或極具爭議課題，校方要求老師「必須以專業角度」考慮議題是否符合學生程度及課程要求，並以持平、客觀為原則，從不同角度分析事件，讓學生培養到理性和客觀思考能力，以表達個人立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%B7%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%A5-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7-14-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%BC%E6%89%A3%E8%96%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%2591%25A3%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258B%2592%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7-14-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%2589%25A3%25E8%2596%25AA%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=882258be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%2591%25A3%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258B%2592%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7-14-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%2589%25A3%25E8%2596%25AA%2F&h=5e657138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%B7%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%A5-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9C%83%E5%8B%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7-14-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%BC%E6%89%A3%E8%96%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"4d309d8670f91284966d6c777c99a9d5e91db205","tid":1811124,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1323e3f1a80193b097259b0e5c1b34f18d59983","tid":1811124,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄局長：抽出害群之馬"},{"pid":"0fd51d0f0a3cf79fdfb7850a9163949fbc468e44","tid":1811124,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d309d8670f91284966d6c777c99a9d5e91db205","tid":1811124,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"無論如何作出咁既處罰<br />\n校長一定係頂住左一定程度既壓力<br />\n抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817e22dd6e7db46073c26d07c747414605f31d7a","tid":1811124,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"元朗副校停左職未<br />\n<br />\n當街叫人屌佢"},{"pid":"c1f5da383bad48293d0604aee0273dca564df396","tid":1811124,"uid":331421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0fd51d0f0